{"tid":1884384,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曾與巴馬丹拿確診員工開會　醫管局一員工喉不適送院","createTime":"2020-02-17T14:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T16:40:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a4400e78f208fc47c4d5aa87a8db6b7d8f168a67","tid":1884384,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"由新型冠狀病毒引起的武漢肺炎疫情持續，本港今日增3宗確診個案，至今本港確診個案累計60宗。其中第57宗個案患者是住在太古城的54歲男子，他在巴馬丹拿集團任職工程師，其45歲同事亦初步確診，二人曾經在本月6日和7日一同到醫院管理局總部出席一個會議。<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局今日（17日）表示，有關會議均在兩名病人出現病徵前舉行，參與會議人士全部都有佩戴口罩，有關調查仍在進行中。而於今日黃昏，一名曾有出席本月7日會議的員工表示喉部不適，將會送院檢查及進行新型冠狀病毒檢測，到於其他的員工均沒有表示不適。"},{"pid":"a1b8328eb02d6d06e0b768d9bdf4ee01efd40817","tid":1884384,"uid":108337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事"},{"pid":"994d6e1c86234fb0cb6ce71ffeeb0dc71204cfaf","tid":1884384,"uid":45285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:28:58.000Z","msg":"中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？！"},{"pid":"3165d700e789faf646079a774310fc5f1dea0bb1","tid":1884384,"uid":75394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c105abd7a1dd27b20e90d43661fd223e7fbb3f","tid":1884384,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"幫佢深喉過?"},{"pid":"96102d7d11ab4ba0e41a5d5c8d71ba207bedf0c4","tid":1884384,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />WSP 都係，兩間都唔洗番工1個禮拜"},{"pid":"c3c878aa6726afb958538b39a03481757a3735a3","tid":1884384,"uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"